description: Deletes tax registration for multiple accounts in batch. This can be used to delete tax registrations for up to five accounts in one batch.

nested_items.name: errors
nested_items.description: The list of errors for the accounts the TRN information could not be deleted for.

nested_items.name: accountId
nested_items.description: The unique account identifier for the account whose tax registration couldn't be deleted during the BatchDeleteTaxRegistration operation.

nested_items.name: code
nested_items.description: The error code for an individual failure in BatchDeleteTaxRegistration operation.

nested_items.name: message
nested_items.description: The error message for an individual failure in the BatchDeleteTaxRegistration operation.
